Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I think doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:39.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They lost their home because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:45.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the uproar has mostly died down,\Nso I don't think there will be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think? Well, I'm sure\NTonya's going to be ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I know he's\Na town boy and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I never imagined that he'd have such\Na hard time getting used to village life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to him,\NChagum's done an admirable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tonya now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:10.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promised that I'd find a place for him,\Nso we're supposed to meet up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect. Take us along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want\Nto ask him to do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some drastic measures\Nare called for here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:26.81,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10\NSoil and Heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drastic measures, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I can tell, he seems\Nto be fitting in well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Chagum isn't the\Nintroverted type, and he's not timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, he's too\Nclever for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, since he was already\Naccustomed to isolation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he would never complain\Neven if he was feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:03:00.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not going to help him\Nlive his life here in town, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unless he becomes a true commoner,\Nhe'll always feel stifled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:14.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I guess the real issue is\Nwhether Tonya will make a good instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They said you were alive,\Nbut you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've put you through a lot of trouble.\NI hope you can forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:45.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that... Just seeing you two\Nalive and well makes it all worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's Saya up to? Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She can master anything,\Nso she can get by anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:58.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a hard worker in the village\Nthat they're bringing her marriage offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're coming back\Nto town anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:09.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We still have all the money that\Nyou gave us, so I thought we'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:15.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I know you just got here,\Nbut would you mind doing a job for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it? Sure, just name it!\NI'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I want you to teach this boy\Nhow to be an errand runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up for it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be all right. I'll be watching nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I guess we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:54.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you don't need to be\Nso tense. It's not that hard a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...\NI just can't seem to get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've got it!\NI just came up with a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, let's pretend\Nthat you're my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:13.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, if anybody gets suspicious, we\Nwon't have to make up any lame excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, call me "big brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rep. Big brother, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious heirlooms\Nfresh off the grill and piping hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heirlooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:43.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a grilled candy that's a mixture of\Negg whites, sugar, and pine nut flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're a favourite of the kids\Nhere in Yogi no Shim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have these on you,\Nyou can get anything you want around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred of these an coins...\Nequals one Fugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:03.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're going to buy a\N40-an bag of heirlooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but just with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that is 10 an short.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like one bag, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 40 an.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to that stand over there,\Nyou can get them for 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The food stand in the alley over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. I think I'll\Nbuy mine over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give one of mine a try,\Nand you'll see! They're delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still... I think I'll go with\Nthe cheaper ones after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:49.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you a special discount\Njust this once! How about 30?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Worked like a charm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did not believe that he\Nwould lower the price so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:04.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn how to do\Nwhat we just did all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it now.\NFor your first time, you did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:21.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're an official resident\Nof Yogi no Shim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess she's\Naround here some place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready for your next lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mon In Zen...so exciting\Nyou'll shout yourself hoarse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:37.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nplace your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mon In Zen. It's what you'd call\Na game of chance. Gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game for grown-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This might count as\Nsocial education too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, place your bets!\NWho will bet a an?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who will bet a copper Fugal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Place your bet, and leave it to\Nthe mercy of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mon In Zen...so exciting\Nyou'll shout yourself hoarse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nplace your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:17.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The man over there spins\Nforeign coins that have a white face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He spins a total of three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and the object of the game is to bet\Nhow many of them will come up heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's one, it's Mon.\NIf it's two, that's In.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If all three come up white, that's Zen,\Nand you get back twice what you bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if three blacks come up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that's called "house takes all"\Nand the house wins everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the final coin\Nis about to be spun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other bets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, this young man is a big better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:53.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have a last-minute bet on Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect place to close the betting!\NThe time for speculation is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's heads or tails...\Nit's up to your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:03.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pray that the coins\Nwill come your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:07.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like this doesn't really make sense\Nunless you try it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's see a Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two whites! In!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's how the game works...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:45.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, place your bets!\NWho will bet a an?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who will bet a copper Fugal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this game, does one have to bet\Nbefore the third coin is spun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:02.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're allowed to place your bet\Nuntil the first coin lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's not as exciting\Nif you wait that long, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be ready to bet\Nbefore he spins the first coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you're never Donna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm such a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many lunches I could've\Nbought from Yogi's with that Fugal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I manna get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were better off losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:28.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NWinning is always better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:32.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is true enough,\Nbut you could not have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:37.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like the coin spinner could make\Nthe coins come up any way he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how could he\Npossibly do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:44.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how could you possibly know that the\Nfirst time you saw the game being played?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know how I know.\NI just know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:59.99,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One white! Mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:18.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? If this goes on, these people\Nwill lose all of their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see that large carpenter\Nsitting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He will most likely lose\Nin the next round as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The old woman over there is\Nwinning for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I suspect that she\Nwill be their next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because she will bet\Nmore than one Fugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FM-More than one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FM-More than one...\NWhen one bets using an coins...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...losing does not seem so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:44.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone who loses a Fugal would\Ndefinitely want to win it back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:50.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But to win back one Iugal, one would\Nhave to win ten bets of 10 han.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:53.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even betting 50 han, one would still have\Nto win twice to recover that Iugal, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, the impulse is not to\Nbet on Mon or Jin, whose odds are 3-in-8...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:02.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but rather to bet on Zen's\Ndouble return in spite of its 1-in-8 odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that person is manipulating\Nthe outcome of the final throw...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...making it so that they\Nmake a profit in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is also why Zen comes up\Nso often when no one has bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:23.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they can really do that, wouldn't that\Nmake this... a rigged game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for those men, it is also their livelihood,\Nso it can't really be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:34.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the majority of the people here\Nseem to be enjoying the gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:40.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If one's objective were to earn money,\Nit would be insanity to play such games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:45.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is difficult to spot individually because\Nof the difference in their wins and losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:48.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But seen as a house-versus-player game,\Neven if the house does not cheat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the odds are so heavily stacked against\Nthese people that they cannot win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:01.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd kept winning, we would've been\Ndriven out of business by one little old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like luck is still on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win for sure next time, just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are,\Nyou big, fat cheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:22.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing dirty!\NRun the game fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do with that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're slandering our good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:33.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand that you're angry\Nbecause you lost all your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but if you're penniless,\Nyou'd better leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:52.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that I could at least\Nkeep them from losing all their money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess it's beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you wanted to\Nrecover your money, Toya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I played with fire, and I got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to help these people,\NI will do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why commoners\Nare looked down upon as fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They delude themselves\Ninto thinking that a game is fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...even when that game\Nis rigged against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, what a bunch of fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This man can make the coins\Ncome up whichever way he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue playing,\Nyou will be the first to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will lose, ma'am.\NAnd then you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are simply letting you\Nwin for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But before you know it,\Nyour pockets will be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:55.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot see through such\Na simple scam, and that is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you will always remain\Nthe ignorant masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who does this kid think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Don't talk like\Nyou know everything, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:11.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's just jealous of us. It's because\Nhis big brother lost his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better hurry home, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll get into trouble\Nwith your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have guts, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as how you're so sure\Nof what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:29.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I assume you can prove that this man\Ncan control what side comes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I shall prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:49.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NYou can't prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa isn't around, either!\NC'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is all right. Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You ready, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One white... Mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have won the argument, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was just one round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet for the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! A double return!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! A double return!\NWe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He can tell how they'll land?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should bet on Jin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. That will not work.\NDo not bet on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one can win this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three black! House takes all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not betting on the last one\Nwas a smart move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:22.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but the money you bet\Non the first throws is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:26.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. You have to tell us.\NHow do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying to know! Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:37.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This man can control the outcome of\Nthe first two coins using the third coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:42.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When he throws the third coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...one can tell the outcome\Nby looking at this man's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When he grips his sash with\Nthe thumb on top, it signals Mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When he grips it with the thumb\Ntucked into the sash, that signals Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:58.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When he clenches his fist, that is\Nthe signal for the roller to produce Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it... That's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:07.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Yogo,\Nwe call that a fixed game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want my money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You damned con artists!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand that you\Nare running a business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But these people are\Nenjoying your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:25.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, please run your games\Naccording to official guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about a one-on-one match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After what you've done, we can't\Nshow our faces around here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's play an\Nall-or-nothing round with no tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw the coins myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:49.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll return all of the money\Nthat we got from these people today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:57.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I win, I walk away with\Nthat necklace of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't do it!\NYou can't bet the necklace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got that from your...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:03.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:13.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won! He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!\NHe did it, he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, I'm not the one\Nyou should be picking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:47.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, brother! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the big brother, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on, mister! Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:02.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was a surprise...\NI thought I was waking a sleeping child...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I might have aroused something\Nmore formidable than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.08,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.71,0:24:45.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toya has disappeared.\NSaya has lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.41,0:24:48.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then Tanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:52.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Flower Wine for Tanda."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11\NFlower Wine for Tanda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:57.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May my prayers reach the border\Nbetween Nayug and Sag...
